<item>
            <title>[MNG-3286] execution.inherited field is ignored</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-3286</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a plugin with multiple executions, one of them I only want to apply to the parent. I set the execution.inherited=false, the execution is still run on all the children.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12794808">MNG-3286</key>
